Author: LowCalPal
Text: It could be a cyst, which is no big deal to treat.  A lump that size calls for a doctor visit for sure, though.

Author: emilyrun79
Text: you can get an x ray to determine if it is a bone or possibly just some inflammation maybe if you bumped yourself or got bit or something. but if it is a bone don't fret! i have an extra bone up there and it is perfectly fine. it is a supraclavicular rib bone. aka an extra tiny rib at the very tippy-top of my spine above the clavicle. i only have it on one side. it's nothing to worry about :)
